Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(300,300)}绝望的雨水  不安的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:37.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(300,300)}那是希望的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:43.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(300,300)}是你笑著告诉了我
