Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(300,300)}不停前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:59.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(300,300)}不完美的世界 闪烁的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:02.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3\fad(300,300)}我们在此相遇
